pan import): Toys & Games|author=|publisher=|accessdate=8 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Capcoms-Vampire-Savior-DarkStalkers-Banpresto/dp/B008HJKNNA/|title=Amazon.com: Capcom's Vampire Savior \u2013 DarkStalkers \u2013 Morrigan DX by Banpresto Medicom 10\" (VARIANT \u2013 Green Hair \u2013 Light Purple Legs \u2013 Blue Bats \u2013 Green Eyes): Toys & Games|author=|publisher=|accessdate=8 September 2014}}</ref> [[Diamond Select Toys]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/toys/2011/12/29/17898/new_diamond_select_toys_now_on_sale|title=New Diamond Select Toys Now On Sale \u2013 News|author=|publisher=Marvel.com|accessdate=8 September 2014}}</ref> E246,<ref name=sultry>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5959393/darkstalkers-sultry-succubus-has-never-looked-so-good |title=Darkstalkers' Sultry Succubus Has Never Looked Quite So Good |publisher=Kotaku.com |accessdate=2014-06-16}}</ref> [[Epoch Co.|Epoch]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/3757_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_6_epoch |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/6 (Epoch) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> HBC-Brote,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/23392_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_h_b_company |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland (H.B. Company) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Heihachi Zazen,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/23395_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_heihachi_zazen |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland (Heihachi Zazen) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/18163_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_5_heihachi_zaze |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/5 (Heihachi Zazen) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Kotobukiya,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/23397_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_lilith_aensland_1 |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 Lilith Aensland \u2013 1/8 (Kotobukiya) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Kurushima,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/23393_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_8_kurushima |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/8 (Kurushima) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> [[Marvel Toys|Marvel]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Marvel-Capcom-Captain-America-Morrigan/dp/B00153AKAG/|title=Amazon.com: Marvel Vs. Capcom Captain America vs. Morrigan: Toys & Games|author=|publisher=|accessdate=8 September 2014}}</ref> Max Factory,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5163981/curvy-capcom-demon-gets-new-figurine |title=Curvy Capcom Demon Gets New Figurine |publisher=Kotaku.com |accessdate=2014-06-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/6605_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_6_nishimura_col |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/6 \u2013 Nishimura Collection (Max Factory) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Mersa,<ref>{{cite web|author=Hiriajuu |url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/60465_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_6_capcom_mersa |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/6 (Capcom Mersa) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Moby Dick,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/101382_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_capcom_queens_02_ |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 Capcom Queens \u2013 02 (Mobydick) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> Modeler's High,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/97614_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_8_modeler_s_hig |title=Vampire Savior \u2013 Morrigan Aensland \u2013 1/8 (Modeler's High) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</re