rrigan_aensland_1_6_utatane_ver_y |title=Vampire Savior - Morrigan Aensland - 1/6 - Utatane ver. (Yoiko Q) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> and Yujin,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/11237_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_sr_capcom_vs_snk_ |title=Vampire Savior - Morrigan Aensland - SR Capcom vs SNK Part 2 (Yujin) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/11214_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_sr_vampire_savior |title=Vampire Savior - Morrigan Aensland - SR Vampire Savior Part 3 (Yujin) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://myfigurecollection.net/item/23948_vampire_savior_morrigan_aensland_1_6_sr_dx_yujin |title=Vampire Savior - Morrigan Aensland - 1/6 - SR DX (Yujin) |publisher=Myfigurecollection.net |accessdate=2014-05-04}}</ref> among many others.\n\nOther Morrigan-themed merchandise include Capcom's wall scrolls and posters,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.e-capcom.com/ec/srDispProductListProductLink/doProductTreeLink/1/1/A10005007/10/10/srDispProductList/ |title=\u30a4\u30fc\u30ab\u30d7\u30b3\u30f3 \u2502 \u30ab\u30d7\u30b3\u30f3\u30aa\u30d5\u30a3\u30b7\u30e3\u30eb\u30b7\u30e7\u30c3\u30d7 |publisher=E-capcom.com |date= |accessdate=2015-08-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.e-capcom.com/ec/srDispProductListProductLink/doProductTreeLink/1/1/A10005007/11/10/srDispProductList/|title=Big Vampire Tapestry / Morrigan & Lilith|publisher=E-Capcom|accessdate=6 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://shop.capcom.com/store/capcomus/en_US/pd/ThemeID.1944700/productID.285166400/Darkstalkers-Movie-Poster-Set.html|title=Capcom Store - Buy Darkstalkers Poster Sets|accessdate=8 September 2014|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904155033/http://shop.capcom.com/store/capcomus/en_US/pd/ThemeID.1944700/productID.285166400/Darkstalkers-Movie-Poster-Set.html|archivedat